WRAP (ENRICHED WHEAT FLOUR BLEACHED WHEAT FLOUR, NIACIN. IRON. THIAMINE MONONITRATE, RIBOFLAVIN. FOLIC ACID. WATER. WHOLE WHEAT FLOUR. CANOLA OIL BAKING POWDER [SODIUM ACID PYROPHOSPHATE, BICARBONATE SODA. CORN STARCH, MONOCALCIUM PHOSPHATE], SALT).
